| 2026-03-26 | Failed to fetch dynamically imported module | 3-layer fix: lazyRetry + ChunkErrorBoundary + vite:preloadError |
| 2026-03-26 | Ably Auth() Warning: token literal | AuthContext: authCallback with proper Ably types |
| 2026-03-26 | TS2769 Ably authCallback type mismatch | Typed with `import type { TokenParams, ErrorInfo, TokenDetails, TokenRequest } from "ably"` |
| 2026-03-26 | ESLint unused event param | Removed parameter entirely `() => {}` |
| 2026-03-26 | Live session notifications not in bell panel | `_notify_students_inapp` creates Broadcast + Notification + push |
| 2026-03-26 | Section dropdown 230 items, no school filter | School dropdown filters sections for ADMIN/PRINCIPAL |
| 2026-03-26 | Students can't unmute/camera in live sessions | `canPublish: true` for all + ControlBar with mic/camera controls |
| 2026-03-26 | Students can only reply, not post in chat rooms | `_user_can_post` now returns True for students in subject rooms |
| 2026-03-26 | "Session has ended" raw 400 error | User-friendly messages + auto-refresh session list |
| 2026-03-26 | Vercel Analytics ERR_BLOCKED_BY_CLIENT | NOT A BUG — ad blocker |
| 2026-03-26 | 503 on dashboard | Render cold start — keep-alive already implemented |
| 2026-03-26 | TS2339 full_name not on UserProfile | Changed to display_name |
