| 2026-03-26 | ESLint setState in effect (whiteboard auto-open) | requestAnimationFrame + ref guard |
| 2026-03-26 | Gemini 429 rate limit — generic error | Exponential backoff retry (2s/4s/8s) + user-friendly message |

